O thou, so thou we long, O thou for help and hope we cry;
We need thy joy â€“ of thou, thy perfect love draw nigh;
Thou hast love is our salvation, thou hast love is our defence,
Thou hast love is our salvation, thou hast love is our defence.

Thy love is enough, O our Lord, thy perfect heart of God;
O thou who will be with us thou, when shall thy love be;
O may we be in thy favour, may we be in thy love,
O may we be in thy favour, may we be in thy love.
